[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    118[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    119[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Returns:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    120[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         Dictionary with pixel_array (numpy), modality, study/series UIDs,
