[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    122[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    123[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Download the DICOM file from S3.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    124[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # In production, this is a real DICOM file from your modality/router.
